rdship","tag-hope-al-rajaa","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-trials-al-balaa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-5pX","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17194,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/15\/dua-door-of-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20829,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Door of mercy for those who supplicate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever among you has the door of supplication opened for him, the door of mercy is opened for him as well. Allah is not asked for anything more beloved to Him than to be asked for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33283,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/22\/tawassul-prophet-dua-in-life\/","url_meta":{"origin":20829,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tawassul: Seeking the Prophet\u2019s supplication in his lifetime","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman ibn Hunayf reported: A blind man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cSupplicate for Allah to heal me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI will supplicate for you if you wish, or it is better for you to be patient if you wish.\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/10\/sufyan-dua-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":20829,"position":2},"title":"Sufyan on Dua: Hardship with supplication better than ease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ruh reported: Sufyan ibn \u2018Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhat a servant dislikes is better for him than what he likes, as what he dislikes compels him to supplicate and what he likes distracts him from it.\u201d Source: al-Faraj ba\u2019d al-Shiddah 21 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062d\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13454,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/08\/allah-pleased-ease-displeased\/","url_meta":{"origin":20829,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ease: Allah pleased with ease, displeased with hardship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Mihjan ibn al-Adra' reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty is pleased for this nation to be at ease, and He is displeased for it to be in difficulty,\u201d and the Prophet said it three times. Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 20\/298 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/hardship-debt-shade-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20829,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Helping others in the shade of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Yasar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would love to be shaded in the shade of Allah, let him help someone in hardship or waive a loan.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad\u00a015520 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41212,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/allah-eases-depression\/","url_meta":{"origin":20829,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Allah eases our sadness as He wills","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, nothing is easy but what You make easy, for You ease the grief of whomever You will.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 974 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064